ass="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-h3czj4">Braambessen</span></div></div></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleMedium mui-118p00q">0,5 bakje</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div role="tabpanel" hidden="" id="ingredients-tabpanel-1" aria-labelledby="ingredients-tab-1"></div><div role="tabpanel" hidden="" id="ingredients-tabpanel-2" aria-labelledby="ingredients-tab-2"></div></div><button class="MuiButtonBase-root MuiButton-root MuiButton-secondary MuiButton-secondaryPrimary MuiButton-sizeLarge MuiButton-secondarySizeLarge MuiButton-colorPrimary MuiButton-fullWidth MuiButton-root MuiButton-secondary MuiButton-secondaryPrimary MuiButton-sizeLarge MuiButton-secondarySizeLarge MuiButton-colorPrimary MuiButton-fullWidth mui-pf85ae" tabindex="0" type="button" aria-hidden="false"><span class="MuiButton-icon MuiButton-startIcon MuiButton-iconSizeLarge mui-j2as55"><svg class="MuiSvgIcon-root MuiSvgIcon-fontSizeLarge mui-1ak19vv" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-testid="mui-icon-copy" data-nosnippet="true"><path d="M16 1H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14h2V3h12zm3 4H8c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h11c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V7c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2m0 16H8V7h11z"></path></svg></span>Ingrediënten kopiëren</button></div></section><div class="MuiBox-root mui-nw3rd5"><section class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-16mdzo2" aria-labelledby="recipe-report-title"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1v7896w" id="recipe-report-title">Zie je een fout in dit recept?</span><a class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-labelLarge ui-link-module-scss-module__unP2SW__link ui-link-module-scss-module__unP2SW__underline-hover mui-mf8xxo" role="link">Een probleem melden</a></section></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-12 MuiGrid-grid-md-6.5 MuiGrid-grid-lg-8 mui-1m3bzj1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-spacing-md-6 MuiGrid-spacing-xl-10 mui-d8san1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1xcwzc"></div><section class="recipe-instructions-module-scss-module__0Wx0yq__instructions MuiBox-root mui-0" aria-labelledby="recipe-instructions-title" id="recipe-instructions-title"><div class="MuiContainer-root mui-15xjimp"><div class="MuiContainer-root MuiContainer-maxWidthXl MuiContainer-disableGutters mui-1v07l17"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-7maqye"><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1ebnygn"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-5t8kbf" data-testid="header"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><h2 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-headlineSmall mui-vf21q9" id="recipe-instructions-title">Instructies</h2></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1smdbud"></div></div></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-13tqxrv" data-testid="instructions-web"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c"><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1kxm50l"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleMedium mui-zd2j1n">Voor de cremeux</h3><ol class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-yggnlh" style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0"><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">1</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Laat de gelatine weken in koud water.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">1 blaadje gelatine</span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">2</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Doe het citroensap, de dooiers, het ei en de bloemsuiker in een steelpan. Klop ze op een zacht vuur luchtig tot de eieren binden.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">85 ml citroensap, 3 eierdooiers, 1 ei, 90 g bloemsuiker</span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">3</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Knijp de geweekte gelatine uit en los ze op in de warme sabayon. Snij de boter in blokjes en roer ze erdoor.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">200 g boter</span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">4</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Giet het beslag in vormpjes. Laat de cremeux opstijven in de diepvries.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86"></span></div></div></div></div></div></li></ol></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1kxm50l"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleMedium mui-zd2j1n">Voor de coulis</h3><ol class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-yggnlh" style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0"><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">5</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Breng het diepvriesfruit met de suiker, de citroenschil en een scheutje Cointreau aan de kook. Laat 5 minuten doorkoken. Haal de citroenschil eruit, zet de mixer erin en zeef alles.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">50 g suiker, citroenen (schil), Cointreau, 200 g blauwe bosbes en frambozen (diepvries)</span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">6</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Laat de coulis afkoelen.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86"></span></div></div></div></div></div></li></ol></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1kxm50l"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleMedium mui-zd2j1n">Voor de bodem</h3><ol class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-yggnlh" style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0"><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">7</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Smelt de witte chocolade au bain-marie. Meng er de gepofte rijst onder.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">100 g witte chocolade, 30 g rice krispies</span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">8</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Giet de chocolade uit tussen twee bakmatjes. Rol het gelijkmatig uit tot een dikte van ongeveer 1 cm.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86"></span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">9</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Laat de chocolade opstijven in de koelkast.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86"></span></div></div></div></div></div></li></ol></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1kxm50l"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleMedium mui-zd2j1n">Om af te werken</h3><ol class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-yggnlh" style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0"><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">10</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Steek een cirkel gepofte rijst uit, even groot als het vormpje van de cremeux. Haal een bolletje cremeux uit de vorm en laat het ontdooien op de bodem van gepofte rijst.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86"></span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">11</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Verkruimel er wat van de wafeltjes over. Werk af met rode bessen, braambessen en coulis.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">50 g wafeltjes (vanille), 0,5 bakje Braambessen, 0,5 bakje rode bessen</span></div></div></div></div></div></li></ol></div></div></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-ns3etz" data-testid="instructions-mobile"><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1kxm50l"><ol class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-yggnlh" style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0"><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">1</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Laat de gelatine weken in koud water.</p></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">2</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Doe het citroensap, de dooiers, het ei en de bloemsuiker in een steelpan. Klop ze op een zacht vuur luchtig tot de eieren binden.</p></div></div></div></div></div></li></ol></div><a class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 ui-link-module-scss-module__unP2SW__link ui-link-module-scss-module__unP2SW__underline-none mui-1pk0apw" role="link" href="/gerechten/cremeux-citroen-bodem-witte-chocolade-gepofte-rijst-rode-bessen/kookmodus"><button class="MuiButtonBase-root MuiButton-root MuiButton-linkGrey MuiButton-linkGreyPrimary MuiButton-sizeMedium MuiButton-linkGreySizeMedium MuiButton-colorPrimary MuiButton-fullWidth MuiButton-root MuiButton-linkGrey MuiButton-linkGreyPrimary MuiButton-sizeMedium MuiButton-linkGreySizeMedium MuiButton-colorPrimary MuiButton-fullWidth mui-1fguu7a" tabindex="0" type="button" aria-hidden="true">Toon alle instructies</button></a></div></div></div></div></section><div class="MuiContainer-root MuiContainer-disableGutters mui-7frf3u"><section class="recipe-review-cta-module-scss-module__HEfrDq__review-cta MuiBox-root mui-1bdm4b7" id="reviews" aria-labelledby="recipe-review-cta-header" tabindex="0"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1h8lqbp"><h2 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleMedium mui-12mspvv" id="recipe-review-cta-header">Wat vond je van dit recept?</h2><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-ldgwgi">Geef je mening en help anderen om de perfecte keuze te maken!</span><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1selwvs"><button class="MuiButtonBase-root MuiIconButton-root MuiIconButton-sizeExtraLarge mui-5d0etv" tabindex="0" type="button" variant="secondary" aria-label="Vind ik niet leuk"><svg class="MuiSvgIcon-root MuiSvgIcon-fontSizeMedium mui-p1f26a" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-testid="mui-icon-thumb_down_alt" data-nosnippet="true"><path d="M15 3H6c-.83 0-1.54.5-1.84 1.22l-3.02 7.05c-.09.23-.14.47-.14.73v2c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h6.31l-.95 4.57-.03.32c0 .41.17.79.44 1.06L9.83 23l6.58-6.59c.37-.36.59-.86.59-1.41V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2m0 12-4.34 4.34L11.77 14H3v-2l3-7h9zm4-12h4v12h-4z"></path></svg></button><button class="MuiButtonBase-root MuiIconButton-root MuiIconButton-sizeExtraLarge mui-5d0etv" tabindex="0" type="button" variant="secondary" aria-label="Vind ik leuk"><svg class="MuiSvgIcon-root MuiSvgIcon-fontSizeMedium mui-x50voy" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-testid="mui-icon-thumb_up_alt" data-nosnippet="true"><path d="M21 8h-6.31l.95-4.57.03-.32c0-.41-.17-.79-.44-1.06L14.17 1 7.59 7.59C7.22 7.95 7 8.45 7 9v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h9c.83 0 1.54-.5 1.84-1.22l3.02-7.05c.09-.23.14-.47.14-.73v-2c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2m0 4-3 7H9V9l4.34-4.34L12.23 10H21zM1 9h4v12H1z"></path></svg></button></div></div></section></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1e1tj8k"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-7muu5a"><div class="sticky-ad-container-module-scss-module__3n6yoW__ad-container"><div class="sticky-ad-container-module-scss-module__3n6yoW__ad"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-16mdzo2"><span class="MuiSkeleton-root MuiSkeleton-rectangular MuiSkeleton-pulse mui-17nggd2" style="width:300px;height:600px"></span></div></div></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-19d7vxe"><div class="sticky-ad-container-module-scss-module__3n6yoW__ad-container"><div class="sticky-ad-container-module-scss-module__3n6yoW__ad"><div class="ad-container-module-scss-module__rcswIG__ad-container ad-container-module-scss-module__rcswIG__default"><div id="ad_rectangle-b1" class=""></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-rr5s5k" data-testid="divider-mobile"><hr class="MuiDivider-root MuiDivider-fullWidth mui-lf33p6"/></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-d47f85"><section class="recipe-instructions-module-scss-module__0Wx0yq__instructions MuiBox-root mui-0" aria-labelledby="recipe-instructions" id="recipe-instructions"><div class="MuiContainer-root mui-15xjimp"><div class="MuiContainer-root MuiContainer-maxWidthXl MuiContainer-disableGutters mui-1v07l17"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-7maqye"><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1ebnygn"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-5t8kbf" data-testid="header"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><h2 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-headlineSmall mui-vf21q9" id="recipe-instructions">Instructies</h2></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1smdbud"></div></div></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-13tqxrv" data-testid="instructions-web"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c"><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1kxm50l"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleMedium mui-zd2j1n">Voor de cremeux</h3><ol class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-yggnlh" style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0"><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">1</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Laat de gelatine weken in koud water.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">1 blaadje gelatine</span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">2</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Doe het citroensap, de dooiers, het ei en de bloemsuiker in een steelpan. Klop ze op een zacht vuur luchtig tot de eieren binden.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">85 ml citroensap, 3 eierdooiers, 1 ei, 90 g bloemsuiker</span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">3</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Knijp de geweekte gelatine uit en los ze op in de warme sabayon. Snij de boter in blokjes en roer ze erdoor.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">200 g boter</span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">4</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Giet het beslag in vormpjes. Laat de cremeux opstijven in de diepvries.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86"></span></div></div></div></div></div></li></ol></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1kxm50l"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleMedium mui-zd2j1n">Voor de coulis</h3><ol class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-yggnlh" style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0"><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">5</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Breng het diepvriesfruit met de suiker, de citroenschil en een scheutje Cointreau aan de kook. Laat 5 minuten doorkoken. Haal de citroenschil eruit, zet de mixer erin en zeef alles.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">50 g suiker, citroenen (schil), Cointreau, 200 g blauwe bosbes en frambozen (diepvries)</span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">6</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Laat de coulis afkoelen.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86"></span></div></div></div></div></div></li></ol></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1kxm50l"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleMedium mui-zd2j1n">Voor de bodem</h3><ol class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-yggnlh" style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0"><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">7</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Smelt de witte chocolade au bain-marie. Meng er de gepofte rijst onder.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">100 g witte chocolade, 30 g rice krispies</span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">8</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Giet de chocolade uit tussen twee bakmatjes. Rol het gelijkmatig uit tot een dikte van ongeveer 1 cm.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86"></span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">9</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Laat de chocolade opstijven in de koelkast.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86"></span></div></div></div></div></div></li></ol></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1kxm50l"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleMedium mui-zd2j1n">Om af te werken</h3><ol class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-yggnlh" style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0"><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">10</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Steek een cirkel gepofte rijst uit, even groot als het vormpje van de cremeux. Haal een bolletje cremeux uit de vorm en laat het ontdooien op de bodem van gepofte rijst.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86"></span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">11</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Verkruimel er wat van de wafeltjes over. Werk af met rode bessen, braambessen en coulis.</p></div></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-mxm51o" style="width:100%;order:1"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodySmall mui-9kgp86">50 g wafeltjes (vanille), 0,5 bakje Braambessen, 0,5 bakje rode bessen</span></div></div></div></div></div></li></ol></div></div></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-ns3etz" data-testid="instructions-mobile"><div class="MuiBox-root mui-1kxm50l"><ol class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-yggnlh" style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0"><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">1</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Laat de gelatine weken in koud water.</p></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1n5khr6" style="width:100%"><div style="width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1jbdk3c" data-testid="recipe-instruction"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-nv3pd6" style="background-color:transparent;border-radius:0;border:none;cursor:default;width:100%"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1ss14ij" style="width:100%;opacity:1;order:2"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1afpkmo"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleLarge mui-12n9hvs">2</span></div><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-direction-xs-row MuiGrid-grid-xs-grow mui-1fzf7xv"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-1ke74kc">Doe het citroensap, de dooiers, het ei en de bloemsuiker in een steelpan. Klop ze op een zacht vuur luchtig tot de eieren binden.</p></div></div></div></div></div></li></ol></div><a class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 ui-link-module-scss-module__unP2SW__link ui-link-module-scss-module__unP2SW__underline-none mui-1pk0apw" role="link" href="/gerechten/cremeux-citroen-bodem-witte-chocolade-gepofte-rijst-rode-bessen/kookmodus"><button class="MuiButtonBase-root MuiButton-root MuiButton-linkGrey MuiButton-linkGreyPrimary MuiButton-sizeMedium MuiButton-linkGreySizeMedium MuiButton-colorPrimary MuiButton-fullWidth MuiButton-root MuiButton-linkGrey MuiButton-linkGreyPrimary MuiButton-sizeMedium MuiButton-linkGreySizeMedium MuiButton-colorPrimary MuiButton-fullWidth mui-1fguu7a" tabindex="0" type="button" aria-hidden="true">Toon alle instructies</button></a></div></div></div></div></section></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-d47f85"><div class="MuiContainer-root mui-15xjimp"><section class="recipe-review-cta-module-scss-module__HEfrDq__review-cta MuiBox-root mui-1bdm4b7" id="reviews" aria-labelledby="recipe-review-cta-header" tabindex="0"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-column mui-1h8lqbp"><h2 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-titleMedium mui-12mspvv" id="recipe-review-cta-header">Wat vond je van dit recept?</h2><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-bodyLarge mui-ldgwgi">Geef je mening en help anderen om de perfecte keuze te maken!</span><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-direction-xs-row mui-1selwvs"><button class="MuiButtonBase-root MuiIconButton-root MuiIconButton-sizeExtraLarge mui-5d0etv" tabindex="0" type="button" variant="secondary" aria-label="Vind ik niet leuk"><svg class="MuiSvgIcon-root MuiSvgIcon-fontSizeMedium mui-p1f26a" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-testid="mui-icon-thumb_down_alt" data-nosnippet="true"><path d="M15 3H6c-.83 0-1.54.5-1.84 1.22l-3.02 7.05c-.09.23-.14.47-.14.73v2c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h6.31l-.95 4.57-.03.32c0 .41.17.79.44 1.06L9.83 23l6.58-6.59c.37-.36.59-.86.59-1.41V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2m0 12-4.34 4.34L11.77 14H3v-2l3-7h9zm4-12h4v12h-4z"></path></svg></button><button class="MuiButtonBase-root MuiIconButton-root MuiIconButton-sizeExtraLarge mui-5d0etv" tabindex="0" type="button" variant="secondary" aria-label="Vind ik leuk"><svg class="MuiSvgIcon-root MuiSvgIcon-fontSizeMedium mui-x50voy" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-testid="mui-icon-thumb_up_alt" data-nosnippet="true"><path d="M21 8h-6.31l.95-4.57.03-.32c0-.41-.17-.79-.44-1.06L14.17 1 7.59 7.59C7.22 7.95 7 8.45 7 9v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h9c.83 0 1.54-.5 1.84-1.22l3.02-7.05c.09-.23.14-.47.14-.73v-2c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2m0 4-3 7H9V9l4.34-4.34L12.23 10H21zM1 9h4v12H1z"></path></svg></button></div></div></section></div><div class="MuiBox-root mui-rr5s5k" data-tes